{"manifest_version":1,"info":{"id":"zain_backup","name":"Zain's Backup","author":"iamzainnnn","version":"v34.1-hotfix","changelog":"V34.1 — Changelogs\n\n- Resolved an issue causing the keyboard to dismiss unexpectedly in DMs.\n- Added a long-press theme picker in DMs for quicker customization.\n- Enhanced the immersive blur effect in Stories for a smoother visual experience.\n- Fixed inconsistencies with notification icons.\n- Introduced Game Hub in the profile section.\n- Addressed issues with likes visibility nudge behavior.\n- Fixed inaccuracies in the unread message counter badge.\n- Improved overall app stability by resolving multiple ANR issues and memory leaks across Reels, Stories, DMs, and media components.\n- Applied additional internal optimizations for better performance and reliability."},"backup":{"78894:":["0: : true","1: : true"],"60946:":["0: : false"],"101311:":["1: : true","0: : true"],"70831:":["15: : true","13: : true","12: : true","11: : false","10: : true"],"69718:":["4: : true"],"105615:":["9: : true","7: : true","6: : false","5: : true","4: : true","2: : true","1: : true","8: : true","3: : false"],"73763:":["15: : true","26: : true","18: : true","13: : true","8: : true","0: : true","21: : true","17: : false","16: : true","3: : true","6: : true","2: : true","1: : true","4: : true","14: : true","12: : true","27: : true","30: : true","5: : true","29: : true","7: : 10"],"106908:":["0: : true"],"77485:":["4: : true"],"103620:":["0: : true","1: : true"],"89057:":["0: : true"],"102713:":["0: : true"],"64040:":["1: : false","0: : false","3: : false","2: : false"],"103969:":["0: : true"],"83747:":["0: : true"],"101226:":["3: : true","1: : true","0: : true"],"106882:":["0: : false"],"96703:":["0: : true"],"101332:":["10: : true","9: : false","4: : true","2: : true","0: : true","6: : true"],"50769:":["23: : false"],"53982:":["0: : true"],"55842:":["0: : true"],"85663:":["1: : true","0: : true","2: : true"],"109190:":["0: : true"],"102290:":["1: : true